er, with\nresults from both methods combined to yield $c_{\\rm vir}>13$ (1$\\sigma$). The\ninferred virial radius is consistent with the limiting radius where the\ncaustics approach zero velocity and where the counts of cluster members drop\noff, suggesting that infall onto A1689 is currently not significant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Oct 2008 11:18:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2009 10:56:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
